org.apache.beam.sdk.expansion

Interface ExternalTransformRegistrar

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DebeziumTransformRegistrar, ExternalRead, ExternalSchemaIOTransformRegistrar, ExternalSqlTransformRegistrar, ExternalTransformRegistrarImpl, ExternalWrite, GenerateSequence.External, KafkaIO.Read.External, KafkaIO.Write.External, KinesisTransformRegistrar, SnowflakeTransformRegistrar, SpannerTransformRegistrar

    public interface ExternalTransformRegistrar
    A registrar which contains a mapping from URNs to available ExternalTransformBuilders. Should be used with AutoService.
